description:
This vintage Christina sweater from the 1990s is a must-have for any nautical or sailing enthusiast. The white and green patchwork design adds a touch of authenticity to your wardrobe, while the cotton blend material ensures comfort and durability. This sweater is perfect for casual occasions and is available in a women's size medium.

The sweater was originally manufactured in Hong Kong and has maintained its originality over the years. It is a unique piece of vintage clothing that will make a statement in any collection. Add this sailing yacht sweater to your wardrobe today and elevate your style to the high seas.
